%% stateful-agents — fencing token timeline (slide 14)
sequenceDiagram
    autonumber
    participant A as Worker A
    participant R as Redis (lock + store)
    participant B as Worker B

    A->>R: SET lock:demo-001 NX PX 30000
    R-->>A: OK
    A->>R: INCR fence:demo-001
    R-->>A: token=42
    A->>A: working… (heartbeat every 10s)

    Note over A,R: network partition — A's heartbeat<br/>can't reach Redis. Lock TTL expires.

    B->>R: SET lock:demo-001 NX PX 30000
    R-->>B: OK
    B->>R: INCR fence:demo-001
    R-->>B: token=43
    B->>R: save(state, fencing_token=43)
    R-->>B: OK (43 ≥ 43)

    Note over A: A wakes up, still thinks it holds the lock.
    A->>R: save(state, fencing_token=42)
    R-->>A: ❌ StaleWriteError (expected ≥43, got 42)
    Note over R: corruption averted. A aborts<br/>and exits cleanly.
